static variables:
1)Decleared inside the class but outside of the method with static modifier
2) scope is with in the class
3) .class loading memory allocated--------->.class unloading memory destroyed


non-heap



clas test
{
static int a=1000;
static int b=2000;

public static void main(String[] args)
{
System.out.println(Test.a);
System.out.println(Test.b);
t.m1();
}

